videos.description: Josh Okogie makes a great cut to get open and finishes with the jam.
videos.headline: Georgia Tech's Okogie cuts backdoor for the slam

videos.description: Ty Jerome drops a perfect pass for a transition bucket and then picks up a steal and layup on the next possession for Virginia.
videos.headline: Jerome does it all for UVA

videos.description: De'Andre Hunter knocks down the triple and gets fouled just before the halftime buzzer goes off.
videos.headline: Hunter gets 4-point play just before first half buzzer for UVA

videos.description: Indianapolis' own Kyle Guy shows off his versatility on the drive and finish.
videos.headline: Guy goes high off the glass for the score

videos.description: Kyle Guy gets the steal and finishes with ease as Virginia starts to pull away from Georgia Tech.
videos.headline: Guy picks off the pass and finishes in transition
